Title: Poppy Austin Retinol Cream(100 ml)
Description: Get ready to lose yourself in a lush, velvety, triple milked Retinol Cream from Poppy Austin. Bursting with essential skin loving vitamins and natural antioxidants, this decadent daily moisturizer contains 2.5% retinol, to protect skin cells from the elements while fending off future damage. A delightful anti-aging surprise awaits in each alluring bottle while rich sheer butter and sweet jojoba oil melt away dryness in lush hydration. For women and men of all skin types, Poppy Austin Retinol Cream is specifically formulated to fight free radical damage and the signs of premature aging. An incredibly lightweight, quick to absorb, non-irritating face cream to diminishes fine lines, wrinkles, age spots and hyper pigmentation. Gentle enough for day and night use, enjoy a plump revitalised skin tone with a youthful dewy glow. Made fresh in small batches each day at our women-owned and operated facility in the USA.

Title: Shahnaz Husain Barbara Cartland - Honey Rose Mint Moisture Plus(40 g)
Description: Pamper your skin with the intoxicating aroma of this natural moisturising cream by Shahnaz Husain. The Shahnaz Husain Barbara Cartland Honey and Rose Cream lets you have baby soft skin along with lustrous complexion. This moisturiser works well on normal and dry skin. Infused with a pleasant blend of organic ingredients like Honey, Rose, Mint, Wild Turmeric, Date and Apricot, this Shahnaz Husain Barbara Cartland Moisturizer nourishes your skin effectively by strengthening the cells. Acting as an anti-septic agent, the Honey essence present in this Face and Neck Cream heals certain conditions like post-acne scars, sun burns and cuts, keeping your skin healthy. Also, with its skin hydrating nature, Honey extract penetrates all the layer of your skin to provide moisturisation, thereby making your skin soft and supple. The Date extract enhances the moisturising property of this Rose and Mint Cream to eliminate all signs of dryness. In addition, you will feel refreshed and energetic all day, as the mint extract found in this organic Moisture Plus Cream reduces the oiliness of your skin and eliminates body odour by adding a minty fragrance to your skin. Moreover, the Wild Turmeric components in this Shahnaz Honey and Rose Cream has natural anti-bacterial qualities that protect your skin from external impurities and pollutants, thereby keeping the skin free of acne, blemishes and pigmentation. Also, the Shahnaz Barbara Cartland Cream has the ability to boost cell revival to make your skin younger looking. You can also attain smooth and even skin tone with the exfoliating action of the Apricot extract found in this natural cream, as Apricot mildly cleanses skin by removing the dead skin layers and imperfections. Attain porcelain complexion by using the Shahnaz Husain Barbara Cartland Honey and Rose Cream. Directions for Use Apply needed amount on the face and neck after bath. Can be used twice a day. Use regularly for best effects.

Title: Shahnaz Husain Shamoist Plus Intensive Moisturising Milk(100 g)
Description: You go out for a walk on a windy day and come back with your skin feeling dry and irritated. To restore the lost moisture into your skin and make it softer, you can use the Shahnaz Husain Shamoist Plus Intensive Moisturising Milk. This organic moisturiser gives you amazing skin in no time. Made with natural ingredients like Aloe Vera Juice, Cucumber Extract, Kheera Beej Extract, Chandan Oil, Chirongi Extract, Madhu, Badham Tel and Wheat Germ Oil, this Shahnaz Husain Shamoist Milk delivers intensive moisturising action. The skin-friendly herb, Aloe Vera in this natural moisturiser maintains the natural moisture balance of your skin while it also keeps your skin free of acne, spots and blemishes. With its cooling effect, the Cucumber extract found in this body moisturising milk soothes your skin to the maximum extent. In addition, your skin will be devoid of scars, burns and cuts as the Chandan Oil contained in this Shamoist Plus Milk is imbibed with natural antiseptic properties. Also, by regulating sebum production in your skin, Chandan Oil has the ability to eliminate the greasy sensation from your skin. Apart from this, the Madhu extract in this organic Shahnaz Husain body milk is rich in antioxidant content which helps boost cell revival, making your skin wrinkle-free and younger looking. You will now have healthy and radiant skin with the nourishing nature of the Badam Tel present in this Intensive Moisturising Milk, as it adds to the natural shine of your skin. Besides, coming with exfoliating properties, the Wheat Germ oil removes dirt particles and the dead cell layers and also tones your skin, making your complexion clear and smooth. This quick-absorbing body milk keeps your skin essentially hydrated for a long while. Get an enviable complexion, the natural way with the Shahnaz Husain Shamoist Plus Intensive Moisturising Milk. Directions for use Apply on clean skin at any time. Leave it on to get absorbed. Use regularly for best results.

Title: Majik Hair Accessories Donuts Bun(Black)
Description: Donut Bun, a donut bun maker, a few seconds for a new hair style. Use it this way : Pull hair back into a ponytail and secure it with a rubber band. Pull the pony through foam donut hole until it comfortably sits on the head. You can secure it with bobby pins if it feels loose. Separate hair into 4 equal sections, and spread them across the donut, until it's completely covered. Wrap and tuck the ends under the foam and pin them down. Spray with hairspray to tame flyaways and set your style. The set of 3 donuts buns with 3 Different sizes 8cm,9cm,10cm.
